entries.journal_entry_description: Deliver the contraband to the fence in the allotted time.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Deliver the container of contraband to Alec in the allotted time.  For this assignment, you must avoid using any methods of travel other than on the ground, the authorities watch the travel terminals and shuttleports like hawks. A bounty has been placed on your head for accepting this assignment, so be on the look out. Do not be surprised if Alec is suspicious that you have been followed. He will only accept the merchandise when he feels comfortable it is safe.

entries.task05_comm_message_text: I was told your skills at this were almost unmatched, perhaps that was bad information.  At any rate, shape up, or I will not deal with you further.
